      <p style="font:18px Arial,sans-serif;color:#cc6600;margin:15px 20px 0 20px">Hi {{customer.first_name}},</p> <br>
      <p style="margin:4px 20px 18px 20px;width:640px">
        We'd like to inform you that unfortunately the invoice of your package with Package ID:<span class="il">{{pkg.id}}</span>,
        that we've just received did not make the cost of the item(s) clear.
        <br>
        <br>
        Hence, we request you to update the same in your <a href="https://staging-member.shoppre.com/locker?bucket=ACTION_REQUIRED">Dashboard</a>;
        so that we can prepare to ship without any delay.
        <br>
        <br>
        1. Visit your <a href="https://staging-member.shoppre.com/locker?bucket=ACTION_REQUIRED">Action Required</a> tab
        <br>
        2. Enter the price you paid for the item(s) in the field provided
        <br>
        3. Select  <b>Submit Item Values</b>
        <br>
        <br>
        Note: You cannot make a Ship Request with us unless you provide the product cost(s).
        <br>
        You can also forward your invoice/attach the invoice of the purchase when you write to us.
      </p> </td>
  </tr>
